Set up claymores
on the left flank.

03:12.691 --> 03:15.210
Did that sound
hollow to you, man?

03:16.611 --> 03:17.811
What?

03:21.491 --> 03:22.851
Wait.

03:34.411 --> 03:38.531
We could be standing right over their
tunnels right now, couldn't we?

03:40.211 --> 03:42.251
