Who are they after?

04:03.372 --> 04:06.692
-Is it 3rd Platoon?
-Captain Hill says Alpha's hit.

04:06.972 --> 04:10.652
-Do they know we're here?
-What do you say, Meserve?

04:11.052 --> 04:15.172
-I'll get it to you ASAP.
-Sergeant Hawthorne!

04:16.372 --> 04:18.732
Set out security to the flanks,
front and rear.

04:18.933 --> 04:21.692
But not too far so they
get separated from us.

04:21.892 --> 04:23.932
Eriksson, take the right flank.

04:24.092 --> 04:27.053
Call Superman 0-2.
We need a fix on the tube.

04:27.252 --> 04:29.532
We'll adjust by the sound.

04:29.733 --> 04:32.412
Superman 0-2, Superman 0-2....

04:58.333 --> 05:02.613
-What the fuck is going on?
-Cease fire!

05:02.853 --> 05:06.214
I saw a gook, sarge.
One of them gooks from the ville.

05:07.334 --> 05:10.174
-You recognizing people?
-I saw him!

05:11.933 --> 05:14.933
The tube's kicking ass on Alpha.

05:15.134 --> 05:16.453
Fuck this!

05:17.054 --> 05:19.694
The tube's got a fix on us!

05:21.014 --> 05:22.654
Oh, Christ!

05:23.013 --> 05:25.734
They found us!
They're walking them in on us!

05:26.654 --> 05:28.454
Superman 0-2, Superman 0-2.

05:29.774 --> 05:30.734
Let's move!

05:31.375 --> 05:35.895
The tube's got a fix on us.
Left flank! Move on!

05:38.654 --> 05:40.695
Silent Twin 0-2, out.

05:42.014 --> 05:43.334
Go! Go!

05:55.254 --> 05:59.695
Oh, Jesus! Oh, Jesus!
Jesus Christ! Oh, God!

06:42.096 --> 06:44.376
-Where's Hawthorne?
-Up this way.

06:44.616 --> 06:47.336
Eriksson's on right flank.
He ain't in yet.

06:50.376 --> 06:53.097
This war's getting old, Mr. Meserve.

06:54.857 --> 06:56.777
Here comes arty!

06:57.696 --> 06:58.896
Fuck!

07:01.297 --> 07:05.736
Oh, shit!
Oh, Jesus!

07:06.296 --> 07:10.976
Okay, Brownie, you get up there with
them. Keep your shit together.

07:13.537 --> 07:18.737
My shit is forever together.
I'm an armour-plated motherfucker!

07:19.457 --> 07:22.177
Oh, fuck! Help me!

07:23.537 --> 07:28.137
Oh, fuck!
Somebody help me!

07:49.258 --> 07:52.018
What's wrong with my arm?
Where's my arm?

07:52.217 --> 07:54.858
-I got something for you.
-You gotta find my arm.

07:55.058 --> 07:59.058
-We gotta move!
-Calm down, soldier!

07:59.578 --> 08:03.658
Help me! Somebody help me! Help!

08:11.898 --> 08:14.699
Here's your arm. Here's your arm.

08:27.898 --> 08:31.339
Somebody help me!

08:32.018 --> 08:33.938
Help! Help!

08:41.899 --> 08:44.499
Help me! Somebody!

08:49.619 --> 08:52.379
Sarge, I need help!

08:52.579 --> 08:56.900
Sarge, help me! I'm stuck!
Oh, I'm stuck. Help me.

08:57.099 --> 09:01.219
-Thank God!
-Pull!

09:07.779 --> 09:09.459
Oh, shit!

09:14.820 --> 09:16.699
I'll put some tracers up there.

09:16.940 --> 09:20.620
-Back me up with the thumper, okay?
-Right.

09:20.820 --> 09:22.100
-Ready?
-Yeah.

09:24.180 --> 09:26.220
Get some, motherfucker!

09:26.500 --> 09:29.620
Get some! Motherfucker!

09:32.140 --> 09:34.420
Yeah, you fuck!

09:36.300 --> 09:38.181
Yeah.

09:50.141 --> 09:53.341
Some mad fucking
minute, huh, cherry?

10:11.501 --> 10:15.342
-We're getting too short for this.
-We ain't short yet.

10:15.541 --> 10:18.902
Thirty days and a wake-up.
We damn near invisible.

10:19.062 --> 10:23.101
You're gonna DEROS out of
this jungle and these clothes.

10:23.261 --> 10:28.222
Put me on that Freedom Bird
and I figure I'm short...

10:28.502 --> 10:31.701
...and maybe
the fucker's gonna crash.

10:31.942 --> 10:34.222
Can you imagine that?
Escape from Nam...

10:34.461 --> 10:37.822
-...to die an airline fatality.
-Never happen, cherry.

10:38.022 --> 10:41.062
You survive the Nam,
you get to live forever.

10:42.902 --> 10:44.742
How long you been here?

10:44.942 --> 10:46.982
-Three weeks.
-Three weeks?

10:47.502 --> 10:49.382
You're breaking my heart.

10:50.622 --> 10:52.822
You know, Meserve,
I've been thinking.

10:53.022 --> 10:56.382
Maybe it's time we stopped
balling these bitches.

10:56.582 --> 10:58.302
We might end up
home diseased.

10:58.502 --> 11:00.463
Dinky dau, man.

11:02.223 --> 11:03.782
The Nam's a trip.

11:03.982 --> 11:07.143
First you don't know shit,
then you don't give a shit.

11:07.343 --> 11:12.263
I mean, you care, but it's just
humpbacked and crooked, you know?

11:12.503 --> 11:15.743
The cherry'll get wasted
because he don't know nothing.

11:15.943 --> 11:18.543
We'll end up in peril because
we don't care about nothing.

11:18.742 --> 11:21.983
-I care, Brown.
-Sure you do.

11:22.183 --> 11:24.943
It's just humpbacked
and crooked, you know?

11:25.943 --> 11:27.663
Clark...

11:27.983 --> 11:31.983
...you and Hatcher and Eriksson
spread out here.

11:32.183 --> 11:34.103
Stay alert.

11:34.383 --> 11:37.543
And don't get lost.
Brownie, let's didi.

11:53.423 --> 11:57.784
Hershey bar number one! Good
stuff. Take a big bite.

11:58.223 --> 12:00.344
Check out this sad ass, man.

12:02.744 --> 12:04.384
Sui?
It's mango.

12:04.584 --> 12:08.584
Quit begging. They don't want your
candy bar. Give it to me.

12:09.424 --> 12:10.624
Cam on ong very much.

12:10.864 --> 12:15.784
Don't eat anything they give you.
Go back where you're supposed to be.

12:17.545 --> 12:19.664
You want to die horribly?

12:19.904 --> 12:22.104
-No, sarge.
-You were gonna eat it?

12:22.345 --> 12:26.585
These people are confused.
Are they Cong or not?

12:26.784 --> 12:30.225
-They're schizophrenic.
-Depends on who scared them last.

12:30.425 --> 12:34.945
You eat some razor blades or
glass in something they give you...

12:35.145 --> 12:37.505
-...what are you dead of?
-Stupidity.

12:37.745 --> 12:40.545
It's a rog, Brown.
Much affirmed.

12:42.705 --> 12:44.065
Yes, indeed.

12:44.265 --> 12:47.785
We're overjoyed to have travelled
11 ,000 miles...

12:47.985 --> 12:50.785
...to assist them in their struggle
to upgrade themselves.

12:50.985 --> 12:54.345
Every one of them is
old or kids. That ain't good.

12:54.545 --> 12:57.986
This is a retirement ville.
Sort of like Florida.

12:58.225 --> 13:02.106
I wasn't gonna eat that.
I didn't want to be rude.

13:02.305 --> 13:04.426
-Rude?
-Yeah.

13:05.266 --> 13:09.545
I'll smack you upside the
head for talking that foolishness!

13:09.746 --> 13:13.346
You do something rude, you say,
"Sorry about that."

13:13.586 --> 13:16.826
For example, you
strangle their chickens...

13:17.026 --> 13:21.266
...cop their rice, or
barbecue their fucking hootch...

13:21.466 --> 13:24.106
...you say, "Sorry about that."

13:24.306 --> 13:27.546
Let me hear you say it.
"Sorry about that."

13:27.746 --> 13:29.786
Sorry about that.

13:30.026 --> 13:32.147
I got something for us, sir.

13:32.386 --> 13:37.546
We asked him which path was safe. One
day he says one, next day the other.

13:38.906 --> 13:42.827
You VC? VC?

13:43.026 --> 13:45.947
Number fucking 10! VC?

13:46.146 --> 13:48.867
-You number fucking 10?
-No!

13:49.227 --> 13:51.347
-You VC?
-VC, no!

13:55.147 --> 13:59.747
All right! We got it!
Number one, old man.

13:59.987 --> 14:03.507
I hope that ain't your
idea of fun, buddy.

14:04.147 --> 14:06.587
This is some
piece of equipment!

14:06.827 --> 14:08.867
Don't look like it to me.

14:09.107 --> 14:12.308
Look like some tree got tangled up.

14:12.507 --> 14:16.267
And this fool gonna tie it to his cow.

14:16.548 --> 14:19.588
Do you know how
one of these things works?

14:19.787 --> 14:22.827
Ain't you supposed to be
hauling water to your pals...

14:23.028 --> 14:26.268
...instead of hanging out with
this motherfucker?

14:26.467 --> 14:28.348
-Yeah.
-So let's go, then.

14:28.547 --> 14:32.868
Right. Okay. No, no, no.
All right. Shit.

14:33.067 --> 14:35.348
Sarge wants us together,
we best do it.

14:36.067 --> 14:38.828
Don't you want to get home
for your own plowing?

14:39.028 --> 14:41.468
-You're married, right?
-Yeah.

14:43.468 --> 14:46.708
Yeah, yeah, come on, motherfucker!

14:52.948 --> 14:56.069
What the fuck
was I talking about, man?

14:57.549 --> 14:59.749
This some bad-ass Thai stick, man.

15:01.348 --> 15:04.709
You got any babies?
That's what I was talking about.

15:04.949 --> 15:07.149
-A little girl.
-A little girl?

15:07.348 --> 15:09.189
Now ain't that my point?

15:09.388 --> 15:12.828
What were you doing back there?
Sarge had to save you.

15:13.069 --> 15:15.269
The ground opened up on me.

15:15.509 --> 15:20.269
I'm hanging there. Half in,
half out of one of the tunnels.

15:20.509 --> 15:24.189
Mortar rounds coming straight
at me. Boom, boom, boom!

15:24.389 --> 15:27.070
-I couldn't believe it.
-Did you pee your pants?

15:27.269 --> 15:29.829
-Don't be shy. Talk to me.
-I'm talking.

15:30.029 --> 15:34.709
You ain't telling me nothing.
Your ass was stuck in a rabbit hole?

15:34.949 --> 15:36.829
So, what happened?

15:37.029 --> 15:38.629
-Man, come on.
-Come on.

15:38.830 --> 15:40.949
Think of me as your priest.

15:41.150 --> 15:43.790
-Lutherans don't have priests.
-Did you pee your pants?

15:43.989 --> 15:47.509
If the sarge hadn't come back
for me, I sure would have.

15:47.750 --> 15:50.590
Without sarge, you ain't
nothing but a sack of shit.

15:50.790 --> 15:53.590
You ain't walking along
jiving with me.

15:53.790 --> 15:58.470
You so much grief bagged and tagged
that your people moan all their lives.

15:58.710 --> 15:59.670
Right, sarge?

16:02.350 --> 16:03.910
Hatch!

16:04.310 --> 16:06.310
-Hatcher!
-What?

16:06.510 --> 16:10.470
You got 30 days to learn
what you can from me and Meserve.

16:12.630 --> 16:13.831
Hatcher!

16:15.150 --> 16:17.270
-Listen up.
-I'm listening.

16:17.511 --> 16:20.511
We gonna DEROS and leave
Freedom Frontier--

16:28.751 --> 16:31.071
One o'clock!

16:36.991 --> 16:38.471
Behind you!

16:44.871 --> 16:47.471
Oh, my God, I hit it!

16:47.791 --> 16:48.911
Sarge!

17:01.912 --> 17:05.752
All right, cease fire! Cease fire!

17:16.992 --> 17:21.872
-I told you this place wasn't safe.
-The bastards set us up!

17:24.112 --> 17:29.032
Sarge, I'm in trouble, man.
I'm in trouble, sarge.

17:29.592 --> 17:33.592
-It ain't nothing, Brownie.
-You sure, man?

17:34.952 --> 17:38.992
It sure feels like something.
It feels bad, sarge.

17:39.192 --> 17:41.752
It ain't nothing, man.

17:43.993 --> 17:47.833
Eriksson, the sarge says
I'm gonna be okay, man.

17:48.033 --> 17:51.313
Oh, yeah. No sweat, Brownie.

18:01.033 --> 18:04.313
Fuck this shit, man!
Fuck this!

18:26.753 --> 18:28.673
Let's go, let's go!

18:29.633 --> 18:31.034
Come on, move it!

18:31.234 --> 18:32.554
Sarge!

18:32.794 --> 18:36.634
Look in my fucking eyes!
I'm gonna hypnotize you!

18:36.794 --> 18:39.274
You're fine.

18:39.514 --> 18:43.554
I know it, man.
I know it.

19:01.474 --> 19:06.555
I'm an armour-plated motherfucker.
I'm an armour-plated motherfucker.

19:07.675 --> 19:09.715
I'm an armour-plated motherfucker.

19:17.355 --> 19:21.715
Sergeant! Sergeant Meserve, you're to
go two clicks back to the road.

19:21.915 --> 19:24.035
APCs are there to
take you to Ap Thanh.

19:24.275 --> 19:28.435
Take a truck back to Wolf.
The company's regrouping there.

19:28.595 --> 19:32.155
-Is that understood?
-You better watch your back here.

19:32.355 --> 19:35.475
This ville is bullshit.
They're harboring VC.

19:35.676 --> 19:38.075
We'll bust some chops
before we leave.

19:38.315 --> 19:41.836
-Don't you worry.
-Torch the fucking place.

20:17.357 --> 20:22.196
Hey, hey, there it is.
My rack, my rack!

20:23.477 --> 20:25.317
So, what are you gonna do?

20:25.476 --> 20:29.717
Get shitfaced and go hump
the brains out of some hos.

20:29.876 --> 20:34.837
-I don't know. I'm too tired.
-Come on. Are we on duty or off?

20:35.957 --> 20:38.197
Let me have a beer.

20:38.437 --> 20:42.757
-No. You should have bought more.
-Give the guy a beer.

20:42.957 --> 20:44.997
-They're mine.
-I'll give you 1000 pi.

20:45.197 --> 20:48.397
-You should have thought ahead.
-10,000 pi.

20:48.677 --> 20:50.157
For one?

20:50.357 --> 20:52.837
Oreos. I'll give you some cookies.

20:53.077 --> 20:56.237
-I was hoping you were still around.
-Forget about it.

20:56.477 --> 20:59.158
We just spent some time
in a combat zone.

20:59.318 --> 21:03.118
The lieutenant had difficulty
getting his head out of his ass...

21:03.357 --> 21:07.958
...and left us in the jungle
like a bunch of crazed motherfuckers.

21:08.638 --> 21:12.718
-What happened to you guys?
-I don't think anybody knows.

21:12.878 --> 21:16.678
-I just about got killed, though.
-What was that like?

21:16.878 --> 21:17.997
I went nuts.

21:18.198 --> 21:19.798
-You wanna shower?
-Later.

21:19.998 --> 21:23.358
Come on, I want to shower.
Let's go shower.

21:26.759 --> 21:30.638
Hey, sarge.
It's the sarge.

21:30.838 --> 21:34.518
This asshole, Clark,
bought one beer off me...

21:34.719 --> 21:39.118
...for 10,000 pi.
Ain't that some shit?

21:39.318 --> 21:42.038
Sarge, are we on duty or off?

21:42.239 --> 21:44.559
-Off.
-Fucking-A.

21:46.319 --> 21:50.078
We've been detailed a long-range
recon in the morning.

21:50.319 --> 21:52.438
We're off till 2100.

21:54.439 --> 21:56.398
Where we gonna go?

21:56.759 --> 22:01.079
The lieutenant will brief me.
I'll brief you guys, 2100.

22:02.839 --> 22:04.439
We're out of here
at 0600.

22:04.639 --> 22:07.199
-We're off till then?
-Yeah.

22:07.399 --> 22:12.319
Sarge, we're gonna take a shower.
What are you gonna do?

22:12.919 --> 22:15.560
I'm gonna go into town and get laid.

22:20.039 --> 22:22.160
What do you hear
about Brownie?

22:23.200 --> 22:25.000
He's dead.

22:31.800 --> 22:36.240
This place is bullshit.
I hate this fucking place.

22:36.439 --> 22:40.920
-They ought to blow it up and pave--
-Fucking-A.

22:42.800 --> 22:46.680
Brownie could make me laugh, man.

22:47.920 --> 22:50.720
And I like to fucking laugh.

22:53.800 --> 22:55.321
You know...

22:56.401 --> 23:01.000
...I never knew a far-out spade dude
like Brownie before Brownie.

23:01.241 --> 23:04.680
They shouldn't make you hump the
boonies when you're short.

23:04.881 --> 23:06.360
They should send you home.

23:06.561 --> 23:09.841
You'd be short when you were close
to where you didn't have to go.

23:10.040 --> 23:12.240
-So what?
-So nobody'd want to go.

23:12.481 --> 23:14.601
I don't want to go now.

23:14.801 --> 23:16.601
They keep moving it back.

23:16.801 --> 23:19.921
Pretty soon they wouldn't
send anybody here.

23:20.121 --> 23:21.481
What's wrong with that?

23:21.681 --> 23:25.361
What I'm saying is these fucking gooks
are shit, man!

23:26.121 --> 23:28.122
They're lowlifes!

23:29.641 --> 23:31.761
Every motherfucker in that ville.

23:32.001 --> 23:35.441
Every man, woman and child knew
about the fucking mortars.

23:35.681 --> 23:39.681
They knew about the snipers,
and they just let them zap Brownie.

23:40.442 --> 23:42.281
They're slugs.

23:42.482 --> 23:47.682
They're roaches, and total destruction
is the only way to deal with them.

24:00.802 --> 24:03.482
Sorry, sarge. Passes are cancelled.

24:03.682 --> 24:04.642
What?

24:05.082 --> 24:08.163
-The ville's off-limits.
-What did he say?

24:08.362 --> 24:11.282
-For how long?
-Indefinitely.

24:13.722 --> 24:15.602
He's serious, man.

24:15.843 --> 24:17.522
Fuck 'em.

24:20.162 --> 24:22.363
-Watch it, sarge!
-Come on.

24:22.643 --> 24:24.683
-Motherfucking--
-Take it easy.

24:24.883 --> 24:26.002
That was easy!

24:26.203 --> 24:29.283
-Motherfucking easy!
-What we gonna do?

24:29.483 --> 24:31.603
Know what this shit's about?

24:31.803 --> 24:36.483
Fucking Cong is in town tonight.
Charlie's in the whorehouse.

24:37.083 --> 24:39.443
-No shit?
-Didn't you know?

24:39.683 --> 24:44.763
Charlie's gotta get laid too.
He works hard killing us. Don't he?

24:47.963 --> 24:52.243
What are we gonna do, sarge?
What are we gonna do?

24:54.323 --> 24:56.523
Goddamn it!

24:59.004 --> 25:01.444
The Cong's getting laid.

25:02.083 --> 25:04.604
And we're just....

25:04.803 --> 25:07.604
It ain't fair, you know?

25:13.004 --> 25:16.004
Am I talking?

25:16.844 --> 25:19.484
I can't tell
if I'm talking or not.

25:22.084 --> 25:24.364
Diaz, how you doing?

25:29.364 --> 25:33.045
Do one of you guys got a Playboy
on you I can borrow?

25:34.364 --> 25:37.484
-Jeez, on me?
-Yeah.

25:37.685 --> 25:40.924
-I gotta find one.
-Somebody sent you a present.

25:41.484 --> 25:44.085
This is Diaz.
He's Brown's replacement.

25:44.285 --> 25:46.924
We're out of here in the morning
at 0500.

25:47.565 --> 25:52.124
I want everyone carrying two frags.
Make sure you got smoke. Sit down.

25:54.085 --> 25:57.245
Leave your vest. I don't want
any heat casualties.

25:57.445 --> 26:00.725
Beyond that, wear what you want,
as long as it's charmed...

26:00.925 --> 26:03.766
...as long as it's helped you survive.

26:04.605 --> 26:07.965
Our destination is Hill 209
in the Tra Khuc Valley.

26:08.165 --> 26:09.526
The hill's here.

26:09.725 --> 26:12.085
There are caves,
there might be VC.

26:12.485 --> 26:16.766
We're looking for tunnels, bunkers,
unmapped trails, whatever.

26:17.005 --> 26:21.925
Now. The orders are we don't shoot
except in self-defence.

26:22.845 --> 26:27.006
You get one of these fuckers
out in the open, you waste him.

26:32.165 --> 26:37.846
We're leaving an hour early because
we detour 2000 metres to the south...

26:38.086 --> 26:40.126
...to the ville of Nghia Hanh.

26:40.606 --> 26:44.446
What we're gonna do is
requisition ourselves a girl.

26:44.686 --> 26:46.966
A little portable R and R.

26:47.806 --> 26:51.487
It'll break up the boredom,
keep up morale.

26:54.487 --> 26:59.046
I want charmed people around me.
So bring your good-luck stuff.

27:02.206 --> 27:03.647
Like this, sarge?

27:07.207 --> 27:08.806
Does it feel lucky?

27:11.047 --> 27:12.167
It looks lucky.

27:12.407 --> 27:14.287
He really say that?

27:15.167 --> 27:17.287
He wouldn't do it, would he?

27:17.767 --> 27:19.887
Bring a girl?

27:20.087 --> 27:23.327
Are you crazy?
As short as he is?

27:23.527 --> 27:27.128
