01:06:01.985 --> 01:06:04.906
He would not tolerate this bullshit!

01:06:05.105 --> 01:06:07.906
Brownie ain't on my frequency no more.

01:06:08.145 --> 01:06:11.665
Brownie's dead.
You on my frequency, motherfucker?

01:06:11.945 --> 01:06:15.306
If you ain't, you're K.I.A.,
just like the gooks.

01:06:16.026 --> 01:06:20.305
Let her go, sarge!
What she gonna do, man? Let her go!

01:06:21.306 --> 01:06:23.706
-Hatcher, waste her.
-What?

01:06:24.026 --> 01:06:26.946
-I'll do it.
-No, Hatcher's gonna do it.

01:06:27.186 --> 01:06:31.026
-Why me?
-You piece of shit. You do what I say.

01:06:31.266 --> 01:06:32.986
I don't want to.

01:06:37.266 --> 01:06:39.266
Choppers, sarge.

01:06:39.906 --> 01:06:41.426
Goddamn it!

01:06:44.746 --> 01:06:46.826
They're gonna see her.

01:06:48.227 --> 01:06:50.066
We gotta get rid of her.

01:06:50.307 --> 01:06:53.147
We'll have every bird
circling this area.

01:06:53.386 --> 01:06:54.706
Diaz!

01:06:55.387 --> 01:06:57.827
-Do it!
-I'll do it, sarge.

01:06:58.067 --> 01:07:01.306
-Diaz is gonna do it. Do it!
-Diaz, no, man.

01:07:01.507 --> 01:07:05.027
-You yellow piece of shit! Be a man!
-Don't do it.

01:07:05.187 --> 01:07:09.147
-Be a man! Do it! Do it!
-Don't do it!

01:07:10.347 --> 01:07:12.987
-Do it!
-Don't let him make you.

01:07:13.187 --> 01:07:15.147
-Don't do it, man!
-Do it!

01:07:15.827 --> 01:07:19.027
Do it!
You fucking piece of shit, do it!

01:07:19.227 --> 01:07:22.827
-Diaz! Diaz!
-Do it! Do it!

01:07:23.027 --> 01:07:25.227
-Do it!
-Diaz! No!

01:07:28.747 --> 01:07:32.508
You don't have to worry
about her coughing anymore!

01:07:47.428 --> 01:07:50.107
Eriksson, you stay here!

01:07:50.348 --> 01:07:52.708
Everybody else move! You cover!

01:07:52.988 --> 01:07:55.108
Now we're in the shit.

01:07:55.548 --> 01:07:59.149
Take no names and count the bodies!

01:08:32.149 --> 01:08:35.589
What the hell is that? Look, sarge!

01:08:37.469 --> 01:08:39.309
It's a gunboat.

01:08:40.868 --> 01:08:42.509
I fixed her, sarge.

01:09:01.590 --> 01:09:04.510
Everybody, move! Right flank!
Right flank!

01:09:04.750 --> 01:09:08.510
Switch with me, Hatch. Go!

01:09:30.711 --> 01:09:34.510
Get some, motherfuckers! Get some!

01:10:08.951 --> 01:10:10.191
Oh, God!

01:10:17.111 --> 01:10:19.552
-She's getting away!
-No! No!

01:10:22.552 --> 01:10:25.232
She's getting away!

01:10:25.792 --> 01:10:27.512
She's getting away!

01:10:27.712 --> 01:10:32.232
That bitch!
I stuck her more than twice!

01:10:37.632 --> 01:10:39.392
Waste her!

01:10:39.593 --> 01:10:41.793
-No! Stop it!
-Waste her!

01:10:45.353 --> 01:10:46.952
Shoot her!

01:10:50.352 --> 01:10:52.112
Shoot her!

01:10:54.552 --> 01:10:56.593
Shoot her!

01:11:19.074 --> 01:11:21.113
Let's make our hat!

01:14:11.077 --> 01:14:13.198
Rowan! Rowan!

01:14:14.757 --> 01:14:17.917
They did it.
We didn't think they would...

01:14:18.158 --> 01:14:20.517
...but they did. They killed her.

01:14:20.677 --> 01:14:23.998
-The girl?
-This ain't supposed to happen.

01:14:26.277 --> 01:14:30.198
We go into this ville.
We just march in...

01:14:30.398 --> 01:14:33.118
...and they take this girl.

01:14:33.318 --> 01:14:35.798
They fucked her and killed her.

01:14:36.078 --> 01:14:37.398
Jesus Christ.

01:14:37.638 --> 01:14:40.638
I mean, this ain't supposed to happen.

01:14:41.278 --> 01:14:43.358
Hatcher's talking....

01:14:43.679 --> 01:14:47.438
Hatcher's talking about Genghis Khan.

01:14:47.678 --> 01:14:50.278
-Meserve said I'm K.I.A.
-And Clark?

01:14:50.519 --> 01:14:51.919
-He's nuts.
-He's here.

01:14:52.319 --> 01:14:56.119
Eriksson, what are you
talking to him about?

01:14:58.079 --> 01:15:00.759
I'm allowed to be talking to him.

01:15:00.998 --> 01:15:04.639
What happens in the field
stays in the field, man.

01:15:04.919 --> 01:15:08.279
You know that. Everybody knows that.

01:15:11.679 --> 01:15:14.799
Clarkie, where's Meserve? Is he back?

01:15:16.759 --> 01:15:20.199
What happened? You disappeared.

01:15:20.759 --> 01:15:22.880
I got choppered out, Clark.

01:15:23.119 --> 01:15:26.320
-We have to regroup--
-Don't pull at me!

01:15:26.519 --> 01:15:28.839
Don't pull at me.

01:15:29.720 --> 01:15:31.520
Reilly said in an hour.

01:15:31.719 --> 01:15:34.439
-I'll be there.
-You better be, cherry.

01:15:34.680 --> 01:15:36.960
Victor Charles Cong is hardcore.

01:15:37.160 --> 01:15:39.720
They said that we were on alert.

01:15:39.960 --> 01:15:42.520
I said, "I am always on alert."

01:15:43.160 --> 01:15:46.840
-Did you see him, man?
-That was freaky, man.

01:15:47.000 --> 01:15:51.720
They get me back in the bush,
I'm coming back in a bag.

01:15:51.960 --> 01:15:54.000
You gotta tell somebody.

01:15:54.800 --> 01:15:56.120
Who do you think?

01:15:56.361 --> 01:15:59.400
-Tell Reilly.
-Hill's the captain.

01:15:59.641 --> 01:16:02.080
You should tell Reilly first.

01:16:02.840 --> 01:16:03.960
All right.

01:16:04.161 --> 01:16:08.561
On the day I was born,
my mama grunted.

01:16:08.801 --> 01:16:12.401
I popped out. Took one look around.

01:16:12.600 --> 01:16:17.120
"Shit," I says,
"it's Two Creeks, Texas."

01:16:18.961 --> 01:16:23.081
So about eight years ago
I'm still in Two Creeks.

01:16:23.361 --> 01:16:26.601
My wife's about to have
our first child.

01:16:26.841 --> 01:16:30.601
I took her to the hospital,
a natural thing to do.

01:16:30.881 --> 01:16:36.041
She was refused admittance to this
hospital on the basis of her race.

01:16:36.801 --> 01:16:41.521
Which is, as you might guess, Negro.

01:16:42.282 --> 01:16:45.722
Next thing I know,
the baby ain't about to wait.

01:16:46.402 --> 01:16:49.321
So my son is born
on the goddamn floor...

01:16:49.522 --> 01:16:52.321
...of this hospital's reception room.

01:16:54.162 --> 01:16:58.322
Eriksson, I flipped the fuck out.

01:16:59.362 --> 01:17:02.522
I started turning over chairs...

01:17:02.722 --> 01:17:04.722
...kicking lamps.

01:17:04.882 --> 01:17:08.122
It wasn't long before I was in jail.

01:17:10.402 --> 01:17:15.242
Now wasn't I on the side
of righteousness?

01:17:20.362 --> 01:17:22.722
So, what was I doing in jail?

01:17:24.403 --> 01:17:28.962
What I was doing, let me advise you...

01:17:29.762 --> 01:17:34.162
...was fixing to shoot some
motherfuckers in that hospital.

01:17:35.163 --> 01:17:37.363
That's what I was doing.

01:17:38.723 --> 01:17:40.563
But you know what?

01:17:41.282 --> 01:17:43.643
It was like they read my mind...

01:17:43.882 --> 01:17:48.883
...and they kept me in that jail
until my mind was turned around.

01:17:49.363 --> 01:17:52.523
When I got out, I only wanted to see...

01:17:52.763 --> 01:17:55.883
...my baby and my wife.

01:18:02.883 --> 01:18:05.843
And I started thinking to myself...

01:18:07.324 --> 01:18:11.723
...what happened is the way things are.

01:18:12.244 --> 01:18:16.523
So why try and buck the system?

01:18:19.644 --> 01:18:21.804
This is what I'm gonna do.

01:18:23.164 --> 01:18:27.964
I'm gonna break up the squad,
send you in different directions.

01:18:29.764 --> 01:18:33.924
-I think this is--
-No, you don't think. You listen.

01:18:34.564 --> 01:18:39.324
You'd best just relax and try
to forget about this thing.

01:18:41.084 --> 01:18:44.844
You can't expect anything else
in the combat zone.

01:18:46.925 --> 01:18:48.924
Is that clear?

01:18:52.925 --> 01:18:56.324
Sir. Yes, sir.

01:19:05.125 --> 01:19:09.724
I got some boneless chicken
I'll trade for some pound cake.

01:19:10.005 --> 01:19:14.525
-We'd kill to keep our pound cake.
-Everybody says that.

01:19:14.805 --> 01:19:18.925
In fact, we have killed
to keep our pound cake.

01:19:27.565 --> 01:19:31.045
If you was me,
what would you have done?

01:19:31.366 --> 01:19:33.325
What do you mean, man?

01:19:34.285 --> 01:19:38.285
I mean, if you were me,
what would you have done?

01:19:38.525 --> 01:19:40.246
I don't know.

01:19:42.726 --> 01:19:45.726
There was this one minute, you know?

01:19:45.966 --> 01:19:48.286
I had this chance.

01:19:49.526 --> 01:19:54.526
I could have got her out of there.
We both could have taken off.

01:19:55.126 --> 01:19:59.806
And then Clark-- What was I
supposed to do? Waste a corporal?

01:20:00.086 --> 01:20:04.007
-No, man.
-Just blow away four Americans?

01:20:04.287 --> 01:20:05.807
-No.
-What then?

01:20:06.047 --> 01:20:08.326
Guys, I can't find my squad.

01:20:10.047 --> 01:20:11.367
Why are you here?

01:20:11.567 --> 01:20:14.886
-I can't find Wilkins.
-Find any pound cake?

01:20:15.127 --> 01:20:18.007
-No, just chicken.
-Where is yours?

01:20:18.247 --> 01:20:21.287
Somebody stole it.
Can I stay with you?

01:20:21.567 --> 01:20:22.927
Yeah, back there.

01:20:23.127 --> 01:20:27.727
I should have gone to Captain Hill.
He'd straighten this out.

01:20:28.007 --> 01:20:32.007
When we reconnoitre to those caves,
do you think--

01:20:32.207 --> 01:20:34.687
Private, move out.

01:20:36.407 --> 01:20:39.447
-You told Reilly?
-Reilly's bullshit.

01:20:39.647 --> 01:20:43.928
No, I gotta see Captain Hill.
He'll square this shit away.

01:20:44.087 --> 01:20:47.127
Don't go around
your immediate superior.

01:20:47.328 --> 01:20:49.928
If I do nothing, she'd just vanish.

01:20:50.127 --> 01:20:52.408
There's a chain of command.

01:20:52.648 --> 01:20:56.287
I wouldn't violate something
so sacred for a murder.

01:20:56.567 --> 01:20:58.887
What are you talking about?

01:21:00.407 --> 01:21:02.528
Don't worry about it.

01:21:04.448 --> 01:21:08.288
I better go. I feel like
I'm doing something wrong.

01:21:08.568 --> 01:21:10.528
I'll see you later.

01:21:13.568 --> 01:21:18.768
You won't see us later if you don't
stop bopping around here.

01:21:20.328 --> 01:21:23.928
Just take it easy, okay? Slow down.

01:21:26.409 --> 01:21:28.368
Tough. There he goes.

01:21:28.609 --> 01:21:32.488
-Pathetic.
-He ain't rendezvoused with his brain--

01:21:34.329 --> 01:21:36.729
Cease fire! Cease fire!

01:21:37.448 --> 01:21:39.129
What's the haps, sarge?

01:21:39.289 --> 01:21:42.648
Booby trap.
Somebody stepped on a toe-popper.

01:21:42.849 --> 01:21:45.089
All right, let's move it out.

01:21:45.329 --> 01:21:48.529
-Who got hit, sarge?
-Cherry.

01:21:48.809 --> 01:21:52.489
That boy was bagged
the minute they sent him here.

01:21:52.770 --> 01:21:55.729
They should have
just shot him at home.

01:21:55.929 --> 01:21:57.729
Okay, let's move out.

01:22:00.889 --> 01:22:03.889
Get your people out of here. Let's go.

01:22:05.329 --> 01:22:07.410
Oh, Jesus!

01:22:16.369 --> 01:22:18.410
Pathetic, dumb-ass Cherry.

01:22:18.690 --> 01:22:20.370
Wait a minute.

01:22:21.370 --> 01:22:24.770
This goddamn thing
is turning us on our heads.

01:22:25.969 --> 01:22:28.130
We're getting it backwards.

01:22:28.330 --> 01:22:31.130
Because every day
is a dose of bullshit.

01:22:31.330 --> 01:22:34.250
Just because we could
all be blown away...

01:22:34.490 --> 01:22:37.650
...everybody's acting like
we can do anything.

01:22:38.250 --> 01:22:40.611
And it don't matter what we do.

01:22:42.330 --> 01:22:47.130
But I think it's the other way around.
The main thing is the opposite.

01:22:47.451 --> 01:22:50.570
Because we might die
in the next second...

01:22:50.810 --> 01:22:54.171
...maybe we gotta
be extra careful what we do.

01:22:54.891 --> 01:22:57.411
Because maybe it matters more.

01:22:59.891 --> 01:23:02.931
Maybe it matters more
than we even know.

01:23:19.572 --> 01:23:23.412
-PFC Eriksson reporting, sir.
-At ease, Eriksson.

01:23:23.652 --> 01:23:26.371
Captain Hill, something happened--

01:23:26.571 --> 01:23:29.172
I'm aware of why you're here.

01:23:29.371 --> 01:23:34.571
Lt. Reilly detailed it to me
just after you brought it to him.

01:23:35.371 --> 01:23:36.932
I didn't know that, sir.

01:23:37.131 --> 01:23:39.732
That just about cover it, trooper?

01:23:39.972 --> 01:23:43.092
I am max-attentive to this situation.

01:23:43.372 --> 01:23:44.932
Yes, sir.

01:23:47.652 --> 01:23:49.932
Is there someone I should speak to?

01:23:50.132 --> 01:23:53.052
Has the investigation started?

01:23:55.612 --> 01:23:59.292
I hope you understand how serious
this situation is.

01:23:59.972 --> 01:24:03.412
Yes, sir.
That's why I reported it, sir.

01:24:03.693 --> 01:24:08.052
This could cause a major international
incident. Do you know that?

01:24:08.572 --> 01:24:10.332
Yes, sir.

01:24:13.133 --> 01:24:15.532
These men fucked up good...

01:24:15.812 --> 01:24:19.173
...but you bringing
formal charges against them...

01:24:19.453 --> 01:24:22.853
...is that gonna help that girl
one little bit?

01:24:25.413 --> 01:24:28.213
Maybe if you had been there, sir.

01:24:29.333 --> 01:24:31.253
If you heard her scream--

01:24:31.493 --> 01:24:36.573
Don't tell me shit about screaming!
I've heard a lot of fucking screaming!

01:24:36.853 --> 01:24:40.253
Most of it's come from
wounded American boys.

01:24:43.774 --> 01:24:47.694
I'm gonna transfer you out
of my company. That okay?

01:24:47.974 --> 01:24:52.654
I'll get you out of the bush,
any fucking place you want to go.

01:24:54.414 --> 01:24:56.894
I saw your 201 file in the rear.

01:24:57.174 --> 01:25:01.333
You volunteered to be a tunnel rat.
Is that what you want?

01:25:01.613 --> 01:25:03.813
I want out of this company.

01:25:04.094 --> 01:25:07.134
Well, that's a rog.
You're a tunnel rat.

01:25:07.374 --> 01:25:10.014
It won't keep me
from bringing this out.

01:25:10.174 --> 01:25:14.294
Nobody's trying to keep you
from doing a goddamn thing.

01:25:14.814 --> 01:25:19.254
My function here is just to tell you
how this will come down.

01:25:19.894 --> 01:25:22.054
And you ought to be advised...

01:25:22.334 --> 01:25:25.534
...that military
court-martials are lenient.

01:25:25.735 --> 01:25:29.375
And stateside review boards
are even more lenient.

01:25:29.614 --> 01:25:33.935
If these guys get convicted
they won't do any real time.

01:25:34.615 --> 01:25:35.735
Yes, sir.

01:25:36.015 --> 01:25:39.975
They'll be out of the stockade
before you know it.

01:25:40.215 --> 01:25:42.695
And if I was them, I'd be pissed off.

01:25:42.935 --> 01:25:46.095
I'd be looking for payback!

01:25:47.095 --> 01:25:51.135
Now, a man like you,
wife, baby daughter...

01:25:51.335 --> 01:25:55.095
...I'd be considering
those factors very carefully.

01:25:57.375 --> 01:26:00.655
Pardon me, sir.
What's your point, sir?

01:26:01.815 --> 01:26:04.376
There ain't no point, Eriksson.

01:26:04.615 --> 01:26:09.375
I'm just illuminating the terrain
in which we find ourselves deployed.

01:26:09.616 --> 01:26:12.535
You don't mind.
And if you do, fuck you!

01:26:12.736 --> 01:26:15.535
-You on my frequency?
-Yes, sir.

01:26:15.815 --> 01:26:18.576
You maggot! Who do you think you are?

01:26:18.776 --> 01:26:21.576
You recommended Meserve
for a Bronze Star!

01:26:21.856 --> 01:26:24.936
He pulled you out of a VC tunnel, boy!

01:26:25.216 --> 01:26:27.175
What he did was wrong.

01:26:27.416 --> 01:26:31.376
But he's a kid.
He's 20 goddamn years old!

01:26:31.616 --> 01:26:36.176
And you're gonna ruin his life?
He saved yours!

01:27:51.658 --> 01:27:54.738
No, man, no!

01:27:56.538 --> 01:27:58.458
Now listen to me, man.

01:27:58.698 --> 01:28:01.938
Just don't get too happy
with those dice.

01:28:02.138 --> 01:28:06.338
-I'll be there in two seconds.
-Okay. All right.

01:28:07.899 --> 01:28:09.938
Hey, Clarkie!

01:28:10.819 --> 01:28:12.459
What?

01:28:53.140 --> 01:28:57.420
-Charlie's in the wire!
-What the hell's going on?

01:28:57.660 --> 01:29:00.020
Christ! What was it?

01:29:00.260 --> 01:29:01.620
Who was on watch?

01:29:01.859 --> 01:29:03.900
Anybody still in there?

01:29:04.180 --> 01:29:06.740
Get that fire out over there.

01:30:03.942 --> 01:30:06.061
You sick son of a bitch!

01:30:15.062 --> 01:30:17.782
I told you, cherry.
What happens--

01:30:24.182 --> 01:30:26.382
Nobody cares, Meserve.

01:30:29.502 --> 01:30:33.102
Oh, I told everybody.
You don't have to worry.

01:30:33.342 --> 01:30:35.262
You don't have to kill me.

01:30:39.822 --> 01:30:42.942
I told them, and they don't care!

01:30:43.463 --> 01:30:45.663
You dinky dau, man.

01:30:46.222 --> 01:30:48.503
You beaucoup dinky dau!

01:31:43.344 --> 01:31:44.944
How you doing, son?

01:31:46.704 --> 01:31:48.144
Sir.

01:31:49.744 --> 01:31:51.424
I'm sorry, sir.

01:31:51.744 --> 01:31:53.184
Drunk, sir.

01:31:53.864 --> 01:31:55.784
Mind if I join you?

01:31:56.624 --> 01:31:58.745
Drunk. Very drunk, sir.

01:31:59.504 --> 01:32:01.224
You going on leave?

01:32:04.584 --> 01:32:08.425
Getting transferred, sir.
Fini boonies.

01:32:10.945 --> 01:32:13.625
This little darling
must be your daughter.

01:32:17.185 --> 01:32:20.704
You're not gonna do anything
crazy with that gun, are you?

01:32:22.905 --> 01:32:25.105
Just protecting myself, sir.

01:32:26.825 --> 01:32:28.785
I gotta protect myself.

01:32:34.065 --> 01:32:36.025
Trouble at home, son?

01:32:38.065 --> 01:32:39.625
Pardon, sir?

01:32:40.385 --> 01:32:45.305
I thought maybe you had problems
at home, sickness in the family.

01:32:49.265 --> 01:32:52.026
The answer's not in that can, son.

01:32:53.426 --> 01:32:56.385
Are you sure, sir?

01:32:56.666 --> 01:33:01.346
I'm a chaplain. Try me.
That's what I do.

01:33:02.586 --> 01:33:05.106
You a chaplain, sir?

01:33:06.386 --> 01:33:09.506
Are you religious, son?
I'm a Methodist.

01:33:12.786 --> 01:33:14.786
I'm a Lutheran.

01:33:16.146 --> 01:33:18.267
We can still talk, can't we?

01:33:28.827 --> 01:33:33.067
I went on a long-range patrol, sir.

01:33:36.707 --> 01:33:40.467
And we kidnapped a girl...

01:33:42.307 --> 01:33:43.947
...from a village.

01:33:47.907 --> 01:33:50.107
And the other four men...

01:33:51.267 --> 01:33:52.627
...raped her.

01:33:53.747 --> 01:33:55.947
And they murdered her.

01:34:00.427 --> 01:34:04.987
And I failed, sir...

01:34:11.787 --> 01:34:13.748
...to stop them.

01:34:34.908 --> 01:34:37.348
Couldn't let it rest, could you?

01:34:37.988 --> 01:34:39.548
You had to push it.

01:34:41.468 --> 01:34:43.149
Go to hell.

01:34:45.028 --> 01:34:46.468
Sir!

01:34:49.508 --> 01:34:53.748
So you don't feel responsible for
the rape and murder?

01:34:57.789 --> 01:34:59.989
No, sir. I don't.

01:35:00.229 --> 01:35:02.669
Is it your feeling, Corporal Clark...

01:35:02.869 --> 01:35:07.149
...that you are wrongly brought
to trial by the U.S. Government?

01:35:12.790 --> 01:35:16.309
I don't have anything
against the government.

01:35:18.110 --> 01:35:21.950
But I just think soldiers like
Tony Meserve and me...

01:35:22.149 --> 01:35:24.509
...belong out in combat...

01:35:24.749 --> 01:35:26.590
...not here.

01:35:27.590 --> 01:35:32.750
Throw us in the stockade and you're
helping nobody but the Viet Cong.

01:35:33.229 --> 01:35:38.510
When Sergeant Meserve called you, did
you go willingly into the hootch...

01:35:40.070 --> 01:35:42.110
...and rape the girl...

01:35:42.310 --> 01:35:43.950
...Tran Thi Oahn?

01:35:46.230 --> 01:35:48.350
Please answer the question.

01:35:51.110 --> 01:35:54.950
Yes, sir. Yes, sir.

01:35:57.830 --> 01:36:02.350
Have you any idea why Eriksson
stayed out of the hootch?

01:36:06.550 --> 01:36:08.910
Well, he was brand-new, sir.

01:36:09.551 --> 01:36:14.950
I was there a lot longer than him.
At least three weeks longer than him.

01:36:15.391 --> 01:36:16.831
You're saying, then...

01:36:17.031 --> 01:36:22.151
...you involved yourself in rape to
avoid being ridiculed?

01:36:25.671 --> 01:36:28.431
When you go out on a patrol, sir...

01:36:28.631 --> 01:36:31.551
...you're not gonna be
as good as you wanna be.

01:36:31.751 --> 01:36:34.631
These guys aren't helping you
do anything.

01:36:35.872 --> 01:36:40.711
There's gonna be four people
on that patrol, and an individual.

01:36:48.032 --> 01:36:52.152
And so I did what I did,
and I got remorse about it.

01:36:55.472 --> 01:36:58.992
But I also got remorse about
talking at this trial.

01:37:00.192 --> 01:37:03.712
I have a loyalty to the men
I was out there with.

01:37:03.912 --> 01:37:06.352
Is it standard for
U.S. personnel...

01:37:06.592 --> 01:37:09.792
...to have sex with
prisoners and kill them?

01:37:09.992 --> 01:37:12.352
-Objection!
-Overruled.

01:37:12.712 --> 01:37:16.392
The prisoner tried to give
away the squad's position.

01:37:17.672 --> 01:37:22.353
She was ill and coughing from the
abuse of you and your men.

01:37:22.592 --> 01:37:25.952
She shouldn't have been there
to jeopardize your position!

01:37:26.193 --> 01:37:28.552
You dragged her out
and raped her!

01:37:28.752 --> 01:37:32.712
And then you blame her for coughing,
so you kill her!

01:37:32.913 --> 01:37:36.033
-Does that about sum it up?
-Objection.

01:37:39.753 --> 01:37:41.273
Well, sir...

01:37:42.153 --> 01:37:44.513
...I've seen a lot of killing...

01:37:45.433 --> 01:37:49.953
...which it's our duty to do,
because it's kill or be killed.

01:37:51.273 --> 01:37:54.953
Sometimes you hate
the enemy so badly....

01:38:01.073 --> 01:38:03.194
About two ops back...

01:38:03.553 --> 01:38:05.473
...Operation Turner...

01:38:05.674 --> 01:38:08.834
...we saw a hootch
that had been burned down.

01:38:09.354 --> 01:38:13.553
Some Vietnamese were carrying kids
out of a bunker.

01:38:13.794 --> 01:38:16.754
They suffered from smoke inhalation.

01:38:17.994 --> 01:38:21.754
I gave one small child
mouth-to-mouth resuscitation.

01:38:23.794 --> 01:38:27.394
That just shows you
we ain't all combat over here.

01:38:31.274 --> 01:38:35.034
Of the charges of rape and
unpremeditated murder...

01:38:35.274 --> 01:38:37.554
...PFC Diaz is found guilty...

01:38:37.754 --> 01:38:41.034
...sentenced to eight years' hard labour.

01:38:42.754 --> 01:38:47.154
Of the charge of rape,
PFC Hatcher is found guilty...

01:38:47.355 --> 01:38:51.114
...and sentenced to
15 years' hard labour.

01:38:51.475 --> 01:38:54.554
Of the charges of
rape and premeditated murder...

01:38:54.755 --> 01:38:57.115
...Corporal Clark is found guilty...

01:38:57.355 --> 01:39:00.555
...sentenced to life imprisonment
at hard labour.

01:39:01.875 --> 01:39:04.395
Of the charge of
unpremeditated murder...

01:39:04.595 --> 01:39:08.475
...Sergeant E5 Meserve
is found guilty...

01:39:08.675 --> 01:39:11.555
...sentenced to 10 years' hard labour.

01:39:12.315 --> 01:39:14.515
Sentences will begin immediately...

01:39:14.755 --> 01:39:18.355
...at Disciplinary Barracks,
Ft. Leavenworth, Kansas.

01:39:18.555 --> 01:39:20.755
Prisoners dismissed.

01:39:27.796 --> 01:39:31.715
If these guys get convicted,
they won't do any real time.

01:39:32.436 --> 01:39:35.356
They'll be out of the stockade
before you know it.

01:39:35.555 --> 01:39:38.076
And if I was them, I'd be pissed off.

01:39:38.276 --> 01:39:40.636
I'd be looking for payback!

01:41:18.759 --> 01:41:21.958
Excuse me. Excuse me, miss!

01:41:22.798 --> 01:41:26.238
-You forgot this.
-Oh! Thank you. Bye.

01:41:33.918 --> 01:41:36.119
Do I remind you of someone?

01:41:39.559 --> 01:41:40.878
Yeah.

01:41:46.479 --> 01:41:49.159
You had a bad dream, didn't you?

01:41:49.679 --> 01:41:51.079
Yes.

01:41:57.840 --> 01:41:59.879
It's over now, I think.

